VALUES (66, 11, E'pgobb', E'password', E'Patrick Gobb (Pat)', 1, E'Civil Engineer', E'pgobb@newfields.com', E'214-755-1891', E'Mr. Gobb has more than 22 years of environmental engineering/consulting experience. He helps clients analyze current and historic site data and explore options that meet regulatory obligation while streamlining the project and reducing overall project liabilities. Specialties include the performance of due diligence investigations (including environmental liability assessments), RI/FS, environmental compliance, risk assessments, soil and groundwater remediation system design and installation, regulatory interaction, and strategic analysis/guidance on Superfund sites. Mr. Gobb \r\nsupports the evaluation and tracking of the USAF Portfolio. He graduated from the University of Oklahoma with a B.S. in petroleum engineering and is licensed in TX, OK.', E'4ce175e0.jpg', E'Gobb 2013.docx', E'', E'', E'', E'', E'2004-11-01', E'2004-11-01', E'972-956-9100', E'PE (TX, OK)', E'0092', 0, 1, NULL);

