VALUES (97, 12, E'ghayward', E'password', E'Gary Hayward', 1, E'Geologist', E'ghayward@newfields.com', E'603-320-6318', E'During his 28 year career, Mr. Hayward has managed and/or directed a diversity of large multidisciplinary environmental programs throughout the United States and around the world. His specialties include environmental impact assessments, environmental siting and planning, and associated environmental permitting and regulatory compliance services for private and public clients. Categories include oil and gas pipelines, field development areas, and terminal and distribution facilities. Among his career highlights, Mr. Hayward has been involved in environmental studies for the National Park Service at Yosemite National Park. He received a B.S. in geology from New England College and an M.S. in marine science from the University of Florida.', E'6dfba59c.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, E'2004-11-09', E'2004-11-09', E'603-672-3379', NULL, E'0576', 0, 1, NULL);

