VALUES (216, 47, E'rwallace', E'password', E'Rebecca Wallace', 1, E'Senior Consultant', E'rwallace@newfields.com', E'704-726-5551', E'Ms. Wallace is a Senior Consultant with NewFields Companies, LLC. Rebecca has over twenty years of environmental consulting experience for both the public sector and private industry.  \r\n\r\nMs. Wallace is a highly motivated and determined client representative and project manager.  She helps clients understand the impact of historic operations on current environmental risks, and the impact of decision making to assist in strategic risk management.  She has worked across the United States, Puerto Rico and the United Kingdom.  Additionally, she has provided research assistance for sites in the European Union.  Her expertise includes areas environmental sustainability, comprehensive site research, environmental due diligence, asbestos risk management, environmental policy/planning development, and teaching/training.\r\n\r\nMs. Wallace has excellent written and verbal communication skills.  She has delivered presentations for venues in the United States, European Union and United Kingdom.   For 12 years, Ms. Wallace was a lecturer providing continuing education for environmental professionals at Georgia Institute of Technology.', E'249cd697.jpg', E'CV RWallace.pdf', E'', E'', E'', E'', E'2007-03-06', E'2007-03-06', E'704-358-0744', NULL, E'0295', 0, 1, NULL);

