VALUES (372, 60, E'afalzone', E'af1872af', E'Anthony Falzone', 1, E'Senior Geomorphologist', E'afalzone@newfields.com', E'415-713-5855', E'Mr. Falzone is currently a senior geomorphologist integrating ecological science, geomorphology, planning, and design to deliver innovative solutions for the sustainable management of rivers, watersheds, and water resource infrastructure. He has over 10 years consulting experience in the fields of geomorphology, environmental planning, and water resource management in California and across the country. His experience includes river restoration, riverfront revitalization, flood management, hydroelectric impact analysis, GIS management and analysis, hydrologic and hydraulic modeling, groundwater/surface water interaction, and field collection of geomorphic data. Anthony Falzone received a B.A. in economics with a minor in forestry from the University of California, Berkeley, and a M.L.A. in environmental planning from the University of California, Berkeley.', E'384bf42.jpg', E'Falzone_Master_NF_Resume_09-23-09.doc', E'', E'', E'', E'', E'2009-09-09', E'2009-09-09', E'510-842-0530', NULL, E'0411', 0, 1, NULL);

